                    </div>
                    <p class="mb-6">
                        The premier workforce management solution for modern enterprises.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex space-x-4">
                        <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-800 hover:bg-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center transition">
